{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "vendor-staff-reg-flow-2026",
    "name": "CloseExp - Vendor & SupermarketStaff registration flows",
    "description": "## Bối cảnh theo code BE hiện tại\n\n- **Đăng ký công khai (`POST /api/auth/register`)** chỉ cho phép `registrationType`: **Vendor** (enum `RegistrationType` chỉ còn `Vendor`).\n- **Không** còn đăng ký trực tiếp `SupermarketStaff` qua cùng body register.\n- **Luồng trở thành nhân viên siêu thị:** đăng ký + xác minh OTP (Vendor Active) → `POST /api/supermarkets/applications` → Admin `GET/POST /api/admin/supermarkets/applications/...` duyệt → user được đổi `RoleId` sang SupermarketStaff + tạo bản ghi quản lý.\n\n## Biến cần chỉnh\n- `baseUrl` (vd: `http://localhost:5014`)\n- `otpCode`: nhập **6 số** từ email sau bước register (hoặc đọc log dev nếu bật)\n- `adminEmail` / `adminPassword`: tài khoản Admin để duyệt hồ sơ\n\n## Scripts\n- Pre-request: sinh email/password unique cho từng folder khi cần.\n- Tests: lưu token, `supermarketId`, assert status cơ bản.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5014",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "otpCode",
      "value": "000000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminEmail",
      "value": "admin@gmail.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminPassword",
      "value": "123456",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminAccessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "vendorFlowEmail",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "vendorFlowPassword",
      "value": "Test@1234",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "vendorAccessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "vendorRefreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "staffFlowEmail",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "staffFlowPassword",
      "value": "Test@1234",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "staffFlowVendorToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "staffFlowRefreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "pendingSupermarketId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "staffAfterApproveAccessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "staffAfterApproveRefreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "A — Vendor only (khách / end user)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "A1. Register Vendor",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var ts = Date.now();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('vendorFlowEmail', 'vendor_flow_' + ts + '@example.com');",
                  "console.log('vendorFlowEmail=' + pm.collectionVariables.get('vendorFlowEmail'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('success', () => pm.expect(j.success).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('message mentions OTP', () => {",
                  "  var m = (j.message || '').toLowerCase();",
                  "  pm.expect(m).to.satisfy(x => x.includes('otp') || x.includes('email') || x.includes('xác'));",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('Nhập otpCode từ email cho email: ' + pm.collectionVariables.get('vendorFlowEmail'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Khách hàng Vendor\",\n  \"email\": \"{{vendorFlowEmail}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"0909123456\",\n  \"password\": \"{{vendorFlowPassword}}\",\n  \"registrationType\": \"Vendor\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "A2. Verify OTP (sửa otpCode trong biến collection)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('success', () => pm.expect(j.success).to.be.true);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{vendorFlowEmail}}\",\n  \"otpCode\": \"{{otpCode}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-otp"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "A3. Resend OTP (tùy chọn)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{vendorFlowEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/resend-otp"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "A4. Login Vendor",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.success && j.data) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('vendorAccessToken', j.data.accessToken || '');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('vendorRefreshToken', j.data.refreshToken || '');",
                  "  pm.test('role Vendor', () => {",
                  "    var r = (j.data.user && j.data.user.roleName) || '';",
                  "    pm.expect(String(r).toLowerCase()).to.include('vendor');",
                  "  });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{vendorFlowEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{vendorFlowPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "A5. Current user (Vendor)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('Vendor profile', () => pm.expect(j.data && j.data.email).to.be.ok);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{vendorAccessToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/current-user"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "B — SupermarketStaff (qua hồ sơ siêu thị + Admin)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "B0. (Tham khảo) GET siêu thị khả dụng — public",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/supermarkets/available",
            "description": "BE không cho đăng ký public SupermarketStaff. Chỉ Vendor; staff sau khi Admin duyệt hồ sơ (`ValidatePublicRegistrationRole`)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B1. Register Vendor (tài khoản sẽ trở staff sau duyệt)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var ts = Date.now();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('staffFlowEmail', 'staff_applicant_' + ts + '@example.com');",
                  "console.log('staffFlowEmail=' + pm.collectionVariables.get('staffFlowEmail'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.expect(j.success).to.be.true;"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Chủ hồ sơ siêu thị\",\n  \"email\": \"{{staffFlowEmail}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"0918234567\",\n  \"password\": \"{{staffFlowPassword}}\",\n  \"registrationType\": \"Vendor\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B2. Verify OTP (dùng otpCode — cùng biến collection, đổi sau A hoặc chạy riêng folder B)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.expect(pm.response.json().success).to.be.true;"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{staffFlowEmail}}\",\n  \"otpCode\": \"{{otpCode}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-otp"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B3. Login (Vendor Active)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.success && j.data) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('staffFlowVendorToken', j.data.accessToken || '');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('staffFlowRefreshToken', j.data.refreshToken || '');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{staffFlowEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{staffFlowPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B4. Nộp hồ sơ đăng ký siêu thị (Vendor)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var ts = Date.now();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('_smName', 'Siêu thị Postman ' + ts);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.expect(j.success).to.be.true;",
                  "var d = j.data || {};",
                  "var sid = d.supermarketId || d.SupermarketId;",
                  "if (sid) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('pendingSupermarketId', sid);",
                  "  console.log('pendingSupermarketId=' + sid);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{staffFlowVendorToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"{{_smName}}\",\n  \"address\": \"123 Đường Test, Quận 1, TP.HCM\",\n  \"latitude\": 10.7769,\n  \"longitude\": 106.7009,\n  \"contactPhone\": \"02812345678\",\n  \"contactEmail\": \"contact_sm@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/supermarkets/applications"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B5. Danh sách hồ sơ của tôi",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.expect(pm.response.json().success).to.be.true;"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{staffFlowVendorToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/supermarkets/applications/my"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B6. Admin — Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.success && j.data && j.data.accessToken) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('adminAccessToken', j.data.accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B7. Admin — Hồ sơ chờ duyệt",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (!j.success || !j.data) return;",
                  "var want = pm.collectionVariables.get('staffFlowEmail');",
                  "var list = Array.isArray(j.data) ? j.data : [];",
                  "var hit = list.find(function (x) {",
                  "  var em = x.applicantEmail || x.ApplicantEmail || '';",
                  "  return em.toLowerCase() === (want || '').toLowerCase();",
                  "});",
                  "if (hit) {",
                  "  var sid = hit.supermarketId || hit.SupermarketId;",
                  "  if (sid) { pm.collectionVariables.set('pendingSupermarketId', sid); console.log('Matched pendingSupermarketId=' + sid); }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{adminAccessToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/supermarkets/applications/pending"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B8. Admin — Duyệt hồ sơ ({{pendingSupermarketId}})",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.expect(pm.response.json().success).to.be.true;",
                  "console.log('Ứng viên cần đăng nhập lại; email duyệt có thể chứa mã nhân viên.');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{adminAccessToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/supermarkets/applications/{{pendingSupermarketId}}/approve"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B9. Login lại — role SupermarketStaff",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.expect(j.success).to.be.true;",
                  "if (j.data) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('staffAfterApproveAccessToken', j.data.accessToken || '');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('staffAfterApproveRefreshToken', j.data.refreshToken || '');",
                  "  var role = (j.data.user && j.data.user.roleName) || '';",
                  "  pm.test('role contains SupermarketStaff', () => {",
                  "    pm.expect(String(role).toLowerCase()).to.include('supermarket');",
                  "  });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{staffFlowEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{staffFlowPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "B10. Current user sau duyệt",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.expect(j.data && j.data.roleName).to.be.ok;"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{staffAfterApproveAccessToken}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/current-user"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "C — Negative / validation",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "C1. Register — registrationType không hợp lệ (JSON)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('4xx', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([400, 422]));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"X\",\n  \"email\": \"bad_enum@example.com\",\n  \"phone\": \"0900000000\",\n  \"password\": \"Test@1234\",\n  \"registrationType\": \"SupermarketStaff\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
            "description": "Enum hiện chỉ có Vendor — giá trị khác thường gây lỗi deserialize hoặc 400."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "C2. Nộp hồ sơ siêu thị — không token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('401', () => pm.response.to.have.status(401));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"No Auth SM\",\n  \"address\": \"1 Test\",\n  \"latitude\": 10,\n  \"longitude\": 106,\n  \"contactPhone\": \"0900000001\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/supermarkets/applications"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}